quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,21,"∆Āe wi'ana guri ma…ď…ďe …óen: "Ko fii honl…óum seeditani…óon e amin?" ∆äe wi'a: "Ko Allah wowlin…óo kala hu'unde On, wowlini men. Ko KaŇčko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka makko kadi ruttete…óon"."
  41,22,"On ngonaani hi…óon cuu…óora, fii wata nan…óe mon, e gii…óe mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on cikkuno, won'de Allah anndaa ko …óuu…ói e ko ngolloton."
  41,23,"Ko …óuum moo…óon, cikkuno…óon Joomi mon, …óuum halki on. Wa…ótin…óon jeyyaa…ďe e pertu…ďe …ďeen."
  41,24,"Hay si …ďe mu√Ī√Īike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe; si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii feleede ngaccitee, …ďe wonaani feletee…ďe accitee."
  41,25,"Min ngurtani …ďe wondii…ďe, …ďeen cu…óinani …ďe ko woni ye'eso ma…ď…ďe, e ko woni …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e ma…ď…ďe, won'dude e mofte yawtunoo…óe ado ma…ď…ďe, immorde e jinna e yim…ďe. Pellet, …ďe laatino hayru…ďe."
  41,26,"Yeddu…ďe …ďeen mb'i: "Wota on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) mbelajo'o, on foolay"."
  41,27,"Ma Min mee…óiniroy yeddu…ďe …ďeen, lepte sa…ótu…óe, Min njo…ďira ko …ďuri bon'de e ko …ďe ngollatnoo noo kon."
  41,28,"Ko …óum woni njo…ďdi a√Ī…ďe Allah …ďeen: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani …ďe ton, njo…ďdi kon ko …ďe yeddiraynoo aayeeje amen …óen."
  41,29,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen mbi'a: "Joomi amen, hollii min majjinnoo…ďe min …ďeen ka jinna e ka yim…ďe, min yaa…ďa …ďe min fuga, haa …ďe wona e …ďur…ďe joltude …ďen"."